author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
🎟️ To come and see Justin Hawkins Rides Again LIVE across the UK from January 2026, find tickets here: 
https://www.aegpresents.co.uk/event/justin-hawkins-rides-again/
🎟️ For VIP upgrades: https://thejawsofvictory.com/pages/justin-hawkins-rides-again?srsltid=AfmBOorryy6x7BKwj8HeKF7R1Jdtat6hl3fNPuhRJfMpQWxpCC2o1IqT

I'm about to take my YouTube show on the road for a second time. Ahead of the tour, I've been speaking to some of the bands who will be my guests at the shows and it's made me realise: I can't keep doing this. I don't want to use my Channel for just reactions, I want it to be something else. I hope you'll stay with me. For everyone who has subscribed over the past five years, thank you. 

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

The latest Darkness album "Dreams On Toast" is here: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/

Get a Justin Hawkins Rides Again T-Shirt & Hoodie here: htt
title: My Channel: I Can't Do It Like This Anymore
